<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>오늘 뭐 먹지? 🐯 고려대 랜덤 메뉴 추천기</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;600;800&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- FontAwesome for Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #8A1538; /* 고려대 크림슨 */
            --primary-hover: #A31D45;
            --primary-glow: rgba(138, 21, 56, 0.4);
            --secondary: #C5A059; /* 골드 */
            --secondary-hover: #D6B26A;
            --dark-bg: #0F0F13;
            --card-bg: rgba(26, 26, 36, 0.65);
            --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --text-main: #F3F4F6;
            --text-muted: #9CA3AF;
            --success: #10B981;
            --warning: #F59E0B;
            --error: #EF4444;
            --radius-lg: 16px;
            --radius-md: 12px;
            --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Outfit', 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--dark-bg);
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(at 10% 20%, rgba(138, 21, 56, 0.15) 0px, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(at 90% 80%, rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.1) 0px, transparent 50%);
            color: var(--text-main);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            padding-bottom: 60px;
        }

        /* Container */
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .logo-area {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD700 0%, var(--secondary) 50%, var(--text-main) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        /* Floating Settings Button */
        .floating-settings-btn {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            z-index: 100;
            background: rgba(30, 30, 40, 0.7);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: var(--text-main);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .floating-settings-btn:hover {
            transform: rotate(45deg) scale(1.1);
            border-color: var(--secondary);
            color: var(--secondary);
        }

        /* Card styles */
        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .card:hover {
            border-color: rgba(138, 21, 56, 0.25);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(138, 21, 56, 0.15);
        }

        .card-title {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: var(--text-main);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .card-title i {
            color: var(--secondary);
        }

        /* Grid layouts */
        .filter-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        @media (min-width: 600px) {
            .filter-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
            .filter-grid-full {
                grid-column: span 2;
            }
        }

        .filter-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .filter-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        /* Buttons toggle styles (custom segmented controls) */
        .segmented-control {
            display: flex;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 4px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            width: 100%;
        }

        .segment-btn {
            flex: 1;
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            padding: 10px 12px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .segment-btn:hover {
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .segment-btn.active {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: var(--text-main);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px var(--primary-glow);
        }

        /* Chips / Badges for Category Select */
        .chips-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .chip-checkbox {
            display: none;
        }

        .chip-label {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            color: var(--text-main);
            user-select: none;
        }

        .chip-label:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        /* Checked represents exclusion! */
        .chip-checkbox:checked + .chip-label {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15);
            border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
            color: var(--error);
            text-decoration: line-through;
        }

        .chip-checkbox:checked + .chip-label i {
            color: var(--error);
        }

        /* Main Recommendation Card */
        .recommendation-area {
            text-align: center;
            min-height: 250px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 2px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            padding: 30px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .recommendation-area.has-content {
            border-style: solid;
            border-color: rgba(138, 21, 56, 0.4);
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(138, 21, 56, 0.1) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 70%);
        }

        .recommendation-placeholder {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .recommendation-placeholder i {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        }

        /* Loaded Menu View */
        .menu-card {
            width: 100%;
            animation: slideUp 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from { transform: translateY(20px); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
        }

        .menu-emoji {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: inline-block;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-8px) rotate(3deg); }
        }

        .menu-name {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: #FFF;
            text-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .menu-tags {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .tag {
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .tag-category { background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3); color: #60A5FA; }
        .tag-budget { background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3); color: #34D399; }
        .tag-distance { background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3); color: #FBBF24; }
        .tag-live { background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3); color: #A78BFA; }

        .menu-address {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        /* Buttons styles */
        .btn-group {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        @media (min-width: 500px) {
            .btn-group-row {
                grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
            }
            .btn-group-three {
                grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        .btn {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            color: var(--text-main);
            padding: 14px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        }

        .btn:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, #610B23 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(138, 21, 56, 0.4);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px var(--primary-glow);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-hover) 0%, #73132F 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(138, 21, 56, 0.6);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
            color: #FCA5A5;
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.05);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.12);
            border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.5);
            color: #FFF;
        }

        .btn-success {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #047857 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-success:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10B981 0%, #059669 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4);
        }

        /* Review Section */
        .review-section {
            display: none;
            animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-out forwards;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .stars-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .star-btn {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            background: none;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
        }

        .star-btn:hover,
        .star-btn.hovered {
            color: #FBBF24;
            transform: scale(1.2);
        }

        .star-btn.active {
            color: #F59E0B;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.5);
        }

        .text-input-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .text-input {
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 12px 16px;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            outline: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .text-input:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--primary-glow);
        }

        .char-counter {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-align: right;
        }

        /* Logs Section */
        .logs-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .stat-card {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 14px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-val {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--secondary);
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 500;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .logs-header-actions {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .search-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .search-wrapper i {
            position: absolute;
            left: 12px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .search-input {
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 8px 16px 8px 36px;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            outline: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .search-input:focus {
            border-color: var(--secondary);
        }

        .reviews-list-container {
            max-height: 400px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            padding-right: 4px;
        }

        /* Scrollbar styling */
        .reviews-list-container::-webkit-scrollbar,
        .modal-body::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 6px;
        }
        .reviews-list-container::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb,
        .modal-body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .review-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 16px;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .review-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        }

        .review-item-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .review-item-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #FFF;
        }

        .review-item-rating {
            color: #F59E0B;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .review-item-content {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .review-item-meta {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .no-data {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* Modal Dialog for Settings */
        .modal-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .modal-overlay.open {
            opacity: 1;
            pointer-events: auto;
        }

        .modal {
            background: #14141E;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            transform: scale(0.9);
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .modal-overlay.open .modal {
            transform: scale(1);
        }

        .modal-header {
            padding: 20px 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(138, 21, 56, 0.15) 0%, rgba(20, 20, 30, 0.15) 100%);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .modal-header h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-main);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .modal-header h3 i {
            color: var(--secondary);
        }

        .close-btn {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }

        .close-btn:hover {
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .modal-body {
            padding: 24px;
            max-height: 70vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .input-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .input-group label {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .modal-footer {
            padding: 16px 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .status-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .status-badge.connected {
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15);
            color: #34D399;
            border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
        }

        .status-badge.disconnected {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.15);
            color: #F87171;
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
        }

        /* Toast Container */
        .toast-container {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            z-index: 2000;
            pointer-events: none;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 400px;
        }

        .toast {
            background: rgba(20, 20, 30, 0.95);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            color: var(--text-main);
            padding: 12px 18px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            pointer-events: auto;
        }

        .toast.show {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .toast-success { border-left: 4px solid var(--success); }
        .toast-success i { color: var(--success); }
        .toast-error { border-left: 4px solid var(--error); }
        .toast-error i { color: var(--error); }
        .toast-info { border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary); }
        .toast-info i { color: var(--secondary); }

        /* Loader Animation */
        .loader {
            border: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-top: 3px solid var(--primary);
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Floating Settings Gear -->
    <div class="floating-settings-btn" id="openSettingsBtn" title="GitHub 및 Google Maps 설정">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-gear"></i>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <header>
            <div class="logo-area">🐯</div>
            <h1>오늘 뭐 먹지?</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">고려대학교 안암캠퍼스 맞춤형 랜덤 메뉴 추천 시스템</p>
        </header>

        <!-- Filters Form -->
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-title">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-sliders"></i>
                <span>추천 필터 조건</span>
            </div>
            <div class="filter-grid">
                <!-- People Filter -->
